data.description: Ready to move in, no wait!  Gated community Featuring a spacious 4/2/2 waiting for its new owner.  Perfect for the family to spread out with this split floor plan. Large master suite and bath with large closet.  Light and bright best describe when you walk thru the front door and see the beautiful floors and wide open spaces.  Kitchen featuring granite countertops, large island open to open family room area.  Behind your home extended brick paver patio and lake view with a fountain.  You can enjoy the resort style clubhouse for fun in the pool and or want to have larger gatherings.  Low Hoa includes internet, cable, and common areas.  Super location close to everything including beaches, Sarasota airport, UTC mall and all conveniences you need.
